                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8631" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2167</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2136 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农业企业如何赋能乡村振兴之佳惠果果绿的商业模式盈利之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How Agribusiness Empowers Rural Revitalization of JIAHUI GUOGUOLV&#39;s Business Model Profitability Road </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李纯青，沈媛</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南佳惠果果绿农业科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">6 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">麻阳冰糖橙；农业企业；商业模式创新；盈利型商业模式；2024百优案例；微案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Mayang orange, Agricultural enterprises, Business model innovation, Profitable business model</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">我国农业一直处于“大国小农”的国情，存在着经营规模小、生产成本高、竞争力弱等挑战，实现农业现代化必须以此国情为基础。农业企业作为新型农业经营主体之一，可以促进小农户与大市场进行有机链接，协调产业链条上的利益主体，形成优势产业集聚，实现农业综合生产效益的提升。本案例以佳惠果果绿的企业发展历程为依据，重点描述其通过商业模式创新的方式完善产业链条、促进农业现代化，降低农业生产成本并实现商业模式盈利的过程。本案例旨在为农业企业提供创新商业模式以实现盈利的思路，尤其是那些进军农业的初创企业和受制于不完善产业链条而无法发展的农业企业。同时，学生通过案例学习也将深刻理解农业企业面临的问题以及商业模式创新对于提高收入和降低成本的重要性，促进商业模式创新相关理论的学习与实践。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> China&#39;s agriculture has always been in the situation of &quot;big country small farmers&quot;, there are small scale of management, high production cost, weak competitiveness and other challenges. The realization of agricultural modernization must be based on the national conditions. As one of the new agricultural management subjects, agricultural enterprises can promote the organic link between small farmers and large markets, coordinate the interest subjects in the industrial chain, form advantageous industrial agglomeration, and realize the improvement of agricultural comprehensive production efficiency. Based on the enterprise development history of JIAHUI GUOGUOLV, this case focuses on the process of perfecting the industrial chain, promoting agricultural modernization, reducing agricultural production costs and achieving business model profitability through business model innovation. The purpose of this case study is to provide ideas for innovative business models to achieve profitability for agricultural enterprises, especially those start-ups entering agriculture and those agricultural enterprises that are unable to develop due to incomplete industrial chains. At the same time, through case study, students will have a deep understanding of the problems faced by agricultural enterprises and the importance of business model innovation for increasing income and reducing costs and promote the study and practice of relevant theories of business model innovation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《创新与创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">价值逻辑下商业模式的要素构成；商业模式与盈利模式的关系；以及商业模式创新的驱动因素和实现路径以及对盈利模式的影响</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
